lass=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-dau-don-vi-tran-thua-tham-thuy-dien-465-189788.html\">HLV Mexico \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u00ec tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/danh-bai-mexico-augustinsson-thach-thuc-dt-brazil-465-189787.html\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hang-loat-ky-luc-sau-tran-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-465-189784.html\">H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp sau tr\u1eadn thua tan t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Mexico</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-421-189776.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/giai-ma-mexico-tai-world-cup-2018-qua-nhanh-qua-nguy-hiem-466-189773.html\">Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 Mexico t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Qu\u00e1 nhanh, qu\u00e1 nguy hi\u1ec3m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-463-189755.html\">Mexico 0-3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (KT): Thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t, El Tri v\u1eabn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng Viking</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br />\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"658","checkdouble":"189794"},{"date":"03:47 28/06","title":"HLV Joachim Low: \"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thua s\u1ed1c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, HLV Joachim Low th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/13.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i khi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-0, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mannschaft g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u00f9ng c\u1ef1c khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-2, c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn trong th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joachim Low th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Joachim Low th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Joachim Low th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i v\u00ec m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Joachim Low th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i: \"\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng gh\u00ea g\u1edbm. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi. S\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3, th\u1ebf n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i\".\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thuy Dien va Mexico la doi di tiep tai bang F World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Mexico l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/HLV-Mexico-dau-don-vi-tran-thua-tham-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Mexico l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111en t\u1ed1i?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp sau T\u00e2y Ban Nha (2014) v\u00e0 Italia (2010). Nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ki\u1ebfn e ng\u1ea1i \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd sa s\u00fat sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y khi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1ecb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1eaft b\u00e0i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Joachim Low kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 e ng\u1ea1i: \"T\u00f4i c\u00f3 ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111en t\u1ed1i cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng \u01b0? T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb gi\u00e0u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 qu\u1ed1c gia tr\u01b0\u1edbc kia, c\u00f2n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n r\u00fat ra b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc-421-189797.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hinh-anh-cau-thu-than-tho-sau-tran-duc-thua-han-quoc-465-189791.html\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eabn th\u1edd sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-han-quoc-chia-se-bi-quyet-danh-bai-duc-465-189786.html\">HLV Shin Tae Yong chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thu-mon-han-quoc-tiet-lo-ly-do-choi-hay-trong-tran-thang-duc-465-189785.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cdv-viet-nam-tai-world-cup-2018-gay-an-tuong-tren-bao-anh-465-189780.html\">C\u0110V Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean b\u00e1o Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-han-quoc-vs-duc-421-189777.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"657","checkdouble":"189795"},{"date":"03:21 28/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Mexico 0-3 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-mexico-03-thuy-dien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed d\u1ef1 World Cup. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n:<br>\r\n- H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c: </strong>Kim Young-Gwon 90+3', Son Heung-Min 90+7' <br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>1. Nh\u1eefng th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Loew</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u \u00edt nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Die Mannschaft t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 ra s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Loew cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1i t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra. D\u01b0 \u00e2m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c 2-0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu sai l\u1ea7m t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c Xe t\u0103ng th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c Xe t\u0103ng th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Diem-nhan-Han-Quoc-vs-Duc-Xe-tang-thanh-cuu-vuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Loew m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u1ec1 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 4 v\u1eeba qua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm th\u1ea5y. V\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng&rdquo; hi\u1ebfm khi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nhau. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Loew cho Mesut Ozil tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t song \u0111\u1ea9y Julian Draxler v\u00e0 Thomas Mueller l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMueller, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 10 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i 2 k\u1ef3 World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. Khi anh \u1edf ngo\u00e0i, Loew c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai-465-189795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai-465-189795.html\">HLV Joachim Low: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Thua s\u1ed1c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, HLV Joachim Low th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Ozil l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Marco Reus, Timo Werner v\u00e0 Leon Goretzka. B\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nhau bao l\u00e2u? R\u1ea5t, r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm khi. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm thay v\u00ec c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i chung chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh c\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c Niklas Sule \u0111\u00e1 thay Jerome Boateng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd chu\u1ec7ch cho\u1ea1c kinh kh\u1ee7ng khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1eabn t\u1edbi h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ee7i h\u1ed5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>2. S\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ecdn s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n l\u00e0 4-2-3-1 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n n\u01a1i h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch l\u00f9i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh th\u1eadt s\u00e2u. S\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, l\u0103n x\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e1ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e1ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/4-diem-nhan-ngay-Han-Quoc-giang-Duc-thanh-cuu-vuong-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 80% (chung cu\u1ed9c 74%). Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n, m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n Die Mannschaft chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa bi\u00ean v\u00e0 trung l\u1ed9 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c xong v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u00fd nhau v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u, chuy\u1ec1n &ldquo;s\u1eeda l\u01b0ng&rdquo; di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 c\u01a1m b\u1eefa. Cho t\u1edbi khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c vang l\u00ean, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 6 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Cho Hyun-Woo ch\u1eb7n l\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eaft chiu t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00ecnh c\u00f3. H\u1ecd d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch g\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ee9c (5 so v\u1edbi 6) v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc-421-189797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc-421-189797.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng F VCK World Cup 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n3. Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda &ldquo;th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u00e9t&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft trong ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR, t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Kim Young-Gwon &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m sau c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1ch Manuel Neuer b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t Young-Gwon l\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i m\u00e9t. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u pha x\u1eed l\u00fd thi\u1ebfu an to\u00e0n. T\u1eeb kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft d\u00ednh qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho t\u1edbi d\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Neuer mac sai lam\" title=\"thu mon Neuer mac sai lam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/thu-mon-Neuer-mac-sai-lam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neuer m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n trong b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang kh\u00e1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft, ch\u00ednh Neuer l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 0-1 trong ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 khai sinh vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ki\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 qu\u00e9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lao th\u1eb3ng l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Neuer l\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho \u0110\u1ee9c b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7, ch\u00ednh anh l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hinh-anh-cau-thu-than-tho-sau-tran-duc-thua-han-quoc-465-189791.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hinh-anh-cau-thu-than-tho-sau-tran-duc-thua-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hinh-anh-cau-thu-than-tho-sau-tran-duc-thua-han-quoc-465-189791.html\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eabn th\u1edd sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eabn th\u1edd sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng, trong khi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Taegeuk c\u0169ng r\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ti\u1ebfc...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ju Se-Jong \u0111\u1eb7t Son Heung-Min v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ebf tru\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Neuer th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y oan \u1ee9c cho Ter Stegen v\u00e0 d\u00e0y th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch HLV Loew. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn Neuer &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m thay v\u00ec Ter Stegen \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a t\u1ea1i Barcelona. Loew \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i canh b\u1ea1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng, \u00f4ng tr\u1eafng tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4. L\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n d\u00e0nh cho nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch k\u00e9o d\u00e0i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m 2002, Italia n\u0103m 2010, T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2014, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 vi\u1ebft s\u1eed l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1n th\u00eam c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c n\u0103m 2018. 5 k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 4 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. L\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc that bai truoc Han Quoc Kroos\" title=\"Duc that bai truoc Han Quoc Kroos\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/4-diem-nhan-ngay-han-quoc-giang-duc-thanh-cuu-vuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ee9c r\u00fat ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u cho s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh vinh quang. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu b\u1ebft b\u00e1t, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 khi World Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga kh\u1edfi tranh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Loew ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ea1i thay \u0111\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c. Sau 5 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u Saudi Arabia. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin th\u00e1i qu\u00e1 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd thua 0-1 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean \u0103n m\u1eebng, ch\u00e2m ch\u1ecdc b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau, ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd ch\u00ecm trong \u00ea ch\u1ec1 t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 0-2. T\u1eeb s\u00e2n c\u1ecf cho t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, Die Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so Han Quoc 2-0 Duc\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Thong-so-Duc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 sau tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-dau-don-vi-tran-thua-tham-thuy-dien-465-189788.html\">HLV Mexico \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u00ec tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-han-quoc-chia-se-bi-quyet-danh-bai-duc-465-189786.html\">HLV Shin Tae Yong chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thu-mon-han-quoc-tiet-lo-ly-do-choi-hay-trong-tran-thang-duc-465-189785.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"656","checkdouble":"189796"},{"date":"03:21 28/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng F VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n- \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 4 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup trong 5 VCK g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t (Ph\u00e1p 2002, Italia 2010, T\u00e2y Ban Nha 2014).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup, sau n\u0103m 1938.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- T\u1eeb khi World Cup c\u00f3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Duc-vs-Han-Quoc-Hector-di-bong.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 bi k\u1ecbch v\u1edbi \"Xe t\u0103ng\"</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n- Con s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch k\u00e9m th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m 2002 (kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i World Cup sau 6 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf 2 trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a World Cup n\u0103m 2018, nhi\u1ec1u b\u1eb1ng 15 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Hy L\u1ea1p n\u0103m 2010.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 8 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Sau 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i World Cup, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Son Heung-Min cho H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (95:52) l\u00e0 b\u00e0n thua mu\u1ed9n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup (kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2010, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup m\u00e0 Thomas Muller kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh (ngo\u00e0i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f2n l\u00e0 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft 2010).<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so Han Quoc 2-0 Duc\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Thong-so-Duc.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 sau tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hinh-anh-cau-thu-than-tho-sau-tran-duc-thua-han-quoc-465-189791.html\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eabn th\u1edd sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thu-mon-han-quoc-tiet-lo-ly-do-choi-hay-trong-tran-thang-duc-465-189785.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cdv-viet-nam-tai-world-cup-2018-gay-an-tuong-tren-bao-anh-465-189780.html\">C\u0110V Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean b\u00e1o Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-duc-vs-han-quoc-463-189757.html\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (KT): Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 chia tay World Cup 2018 ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"655","checkdouble":"189797"},{"date":"04:34 28/06","title":"HLV Mladen Krstajic: \"Serbia ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n Brazil trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hlv-serbia-khang-dinh-choi-tren-chan-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u1eddi World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua Brazil, HLV Mladen Krstajic cho r\u1eb1ng Serbia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia-461-189793.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia-461-189793.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 0-2 Brazil (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Selecao ch\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Serbia. H\u1ecd \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Serbia chia tay World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng Costa Rica v\u00e0 thua Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, \u0110T Serbia bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng Brazil trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Serbia kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Selecao \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-2.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Serbia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Serbia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/hlv-serbia-khang-dinh-choi-tren-chan-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Serbia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n Brazil trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPaulinho v\u00e0 Thiago Silva l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho Brazil. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Serbia v\u00e0 Costa Rica c\u00f9ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, Brazil v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Mladen Krstajic cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, Brazil l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: \"Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u00e0 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ebf, \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i v\u00e0 Brazil ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Mladen Krstajic ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua Brazil, HLV Mladen Krstajic ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i cho r\u1eb1ng Serbia l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n: \"T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng Serbia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, ngo\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Brazil. \u0110\u00f3 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\u0110\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p hai, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn r\u1ee7i ro, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Brazil, c\u0169ng xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00ec nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m trong th\u1eddi gian qua\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn HLV Krstajic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Serbia ph\u1ea3i \u01b0u ti\u00ean t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-serbia-463-189782.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-brazil-vs-serbia-463-189782.html\">Serbia 0-2 Brazil (KT): D\u1ea1o ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Moscow, Selecao k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Selecao ch\u1eb3ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Serbia. H\u1ecd \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"654","checkdouble":"189798"},{"date":"05:42 28/06","title":"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e1ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/4-diem-nhan-ngay-han-quoc-giang-duc-thanh-cuu-vuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed d\u1ef1 World Cup. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 sa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n:<br>\r\n- H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c: </strong>Kim Young-Gwon 90+3', Son Heung-Min 90+7' <br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>1. Nh\u1eefng th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Loew</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1u \u00edt nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Die Mannschaft t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 ra s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Loew cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1i t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra. D\u01b0 \u00e2m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c 2-0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu sai l\u1ea7m t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c Xe t\u0103ng th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c Xe t\u0103ng th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Diem-nhan-Han-Quoc-vs-Duc-Xe-tang-thanh-cuu-vuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Loew m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u1ec1 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 4 v\u1eeba qua, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm th\u1ea5y. V\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng&rdquo; hi\u1ebfm khi ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nhau. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Loew cho Mesut Ozil tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t song \u0111\u1ea9y Julian Draxler v\u00e0 Thomas Mueller l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMueller, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 10 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i 2 k\u1ef3 World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c. Khi anh \u1edf ngo\u00e0i, Loew c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai-465-189795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai-465-189795.html\">HLV Joachim Low: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\n<span>Thua s\u1ed1c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, HLV Joachim Low th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i khi tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Ozil l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Marco Reus, Timo Werner v\u00e0 Leon Goretzka. B\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nhau bao l\u00e2u? R\u1ea5t, r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm khi. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm thay v\u00ec c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i chung chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh c\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c Niklas Sule \u0111\u00e1 thay Jerome Boateng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd chu\u1ec7ch cho\u1ea1c kinh kh\u1ee7ng khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1eabn t\u1edbi h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ee7i h\u1ed5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>2. S\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ecdn s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n l\u00e0 4-2-3-1 nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n n\u01a1i h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch l\u00f9i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh th\u1eadt s\u00e2u. S\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, l\u0103n x\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc kh\u00f4ng l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e1ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ng\u00e0y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00e1ng \u0110\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/4-diem-nhan-ngay-Han-Quoc-giang-Duc-thanh-cuu-vuong-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 80% (chung cu\u1ed9c 74%). Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n, m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n Die Mannschaft chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa bi\u00ean v\u00e0 trung l\u1ed9 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c xong v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u00fd nhau v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u, chuy\u1ec1n &ldquo;s\u1eeda l\u01b0ng&rdquo; di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 c\u01a1m b\u1eefa. Cho t\u1edbi khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c vang l\u00ean, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 6 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Cho Hyun-Woo ch\u1eb7n l\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eaft chiu t\u1ed1i \u0111a nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00ecnh c\u00f3. H\u1ecd d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch g\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ee9c (5 so v\u1edbi 6) v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc-421-189797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-duc-02-han-quoc-421-189797.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 0-2 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng F VCK World Cup 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n3. Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda &ldquo;th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u00e9t&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft trong ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR, t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh Kim Young-Gwon &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m sau c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 Toni Kroos c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1ch Manuel Neuer b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t Young-Gwon l\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i m\u00e9t. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u pha x\u1eed l\u00fd thi\u1ebfu an to\u00e0n. T\u1eeb kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft d\u00ednh qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho t\u1edbi d\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Neuer mac sai lam\" title=\"thu mon Neuer mac sai lam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/thu-mon-Neuer-mac-sai-lam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neuer m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n trong b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang kh\u00e1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft, ch\u00ednh Neuer l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 0-1 trong ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 khai sinh vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ki\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 qu\u00e9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lao th\u1eb3ng l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Neuer l\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho \u0110\u1ee9c b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7, ch\u00ednh anh l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hinh-anh-cau-thu-than-tho-sau-tran-duc-thua-han-quoc-465-189791.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hinh-anh-cau-thu-than-tho-sau-tran-duc-thua-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hinh-anh-cau-thu-than-tho-sau-tran-duc-thua-han-quoc-465-189791.html\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eabn th\u1edd sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\n<span>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eabn th\u1edd sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng, trong khi nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Taegeuk c\u0169ng r\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ti\u1ebfc...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ju Se-Jong \u0111\u1eb7t Son Heung-Min v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 khung th\u00e0nh b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ebf tru\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Neuer th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y oan \u1ee9c cho Ter Stegen v\u00e0 d\u00e0y th\u00eam nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch HLV Loew. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110\u1ee9c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn Neuer &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m thay v\u00ec Ter Stegen \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a t\u1ea1i Barcelona. Loew \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i canh b\u1ea1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng, \u00f4ng tr\u1eafng tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>4. L\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n d\u00e0nh cho nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch k\u00e9o d\u00e0i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau Ph\u00e1p n\u0103m 2002, Italia n\u0103m 2010, T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2014, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 vi\u1ebft s\u1eed l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1n th\u00eam c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c n\u0103m 2018. 5 k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 4 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. L\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc that bai truoc Han Quoc Kroos\" title=\"Duc that bai truoc Han Quoc Kroos\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/4-diem-nhan-ngay-han-quoc-giang-duc-thanh-cuu-vuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ee9c r\u00fat ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9c ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u cho s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh vinh quang. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu b\u1ebft b\u00e1t, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 khi World Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga kh\u1edfi tranh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Loew ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ea1i thay \u0111\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c. Sau 5 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u00e1t n\u00fat 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u Saudi Arabia. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin th\u00e1i qu\u00e1 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd thua 0-1 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ed3n nhi\u00ean \u0103n m\u1eebng, ch\u00e2m ch\u1ecdc b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau, ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd ch\u00ecm trong \u00ea ch\u1ec1 t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 0-2. T\u1eeb s\u00e2n c\u1ecf cho t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, Die Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so Han Quoc 2-0 Duc\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Thong-so-Duc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 sau tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mexico-dau-don-vi-tran-thua-tham-thuy-dien-465-189788.html\">HLV Mexico \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u00ec tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u00f9 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-han-quoc-chia-se-bi-quyet-danh-bai-duc-465-189786.html\">HLV Shin Tae Yong chia s\u1ebb b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thu-mon-han-quoc-tiet-lo-ly-do-choi-hay-trong-tran-thang-duc-465-189785.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-han-quoc-461-189779.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"653","checkdouble":"189799"},{"date":"05:39 28/06","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn thua nh\u1ee5c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/huyen-thoai-chi-trich-dt-duc-sau-tran-thua-nhuc-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Dietmar Hamann \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng b\u1edfi tay H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 Hamann ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 Hamann ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/huyen-thoai-chi-trich-dt-duc-sau-tran-thua-nhuc-han-quoc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110T\u00a0\u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng F <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a \u201cC\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng\u201d v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Die Mannschaft kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 qu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng phung ph\u00ed r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Kim Young-Gwon \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5. Vi\u1ec7c Neuer b\u1ecf g\u00f4n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua n\u1eefa khi Son Heung-min tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i s\u00fat b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Hamann ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 Dietmar Hamann cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u1edf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Manuel Neuer l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua n\u1eefa th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong 4 hay 5 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i t\u1eebng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Euro (n\u0103m 2004). Nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u00e2y gi\u1edd th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 huy, h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1a d\u1eabm khi l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cN\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang ta t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Confederations Cup. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c sau khi \u0110T\u00a0\u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai-465-189795.html\">HLV Joachim Low: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hinh-anh-cau-thu-than-tho-sau-tran-duc-thua-han-quoc-465-189791.html\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eabn th\u1edd sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"652","checkdouble":"189800"},{"date":"05:54 28/06","title":"Hummels: \"\u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hummels-duc-da-choi-te-dan-deu-tu-nam-2017.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mats Hummels cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 d\u1ea7n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2017.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1938. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Die Mannschaft c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1y b\u1ea3ng F <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> sau tr\u1eadn thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i Kazan h\u00f4m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hummels\" title=\"Hummels\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/hummels-duc-da-choi-te-dan-deu-tu-nam-2017.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hummels bu\u1ed3n r\u1ea7u n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHummels \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Timo Werner v\u00e0 Toni Kroos \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, &ldquo;C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn hai c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea5m tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng t\u1eeb Kim Young-gwon v\u00e0 Son Heung-min.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ngay trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. V\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Toni Kroos \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+5, \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. <br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hummels bu\u1ed3n r\u1ea7u</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Hummels cho r\u1eb1ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0o thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac th\u00e0nh l\u1eddi v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tin \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau khi b\u1ecb thua 0-1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. Th\u1eadt ra, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 pha b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat 87. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 ngay sau \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i c\u00f4ng khai nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a thu n\u0103m 2017. V\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 xa r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng cay \u0111\u1eafng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau c\u00fa s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T&nbsp;\u0110\u1ee9c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-chi-trich-dt-duc-sau-tran-thua-nhuc-han-quoc-469-189800.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn thua nh\u1ee5c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/joachim-low-thua-nhan-duc-dang-bi-loai-465-189795.html\">HLV Joachim Low: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"651","checkdouble":"189802"},{"date":"06:08 28/06","title":"Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Brazil v\u00e0 Serbia \u0111\u00eam qua v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><h2>Marcelo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Brazil \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Serbia. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed khi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Tite c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcelo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Brazil lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marcelo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Brazil lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Marcelo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Serbia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 10 ph\u00fat sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u1ed5i h\u1ed3i c\u00f2i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n v\u1ebft \u0111au ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y. V\u00e0 Marcelo nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c cho Brazil \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng E <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMarcelo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp t\u1ec5nh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf. V\u00e0 HLV Tite \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Filipe Luis v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Marcelo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Brazil</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb co th\u1eaft c\u01a1 l\u01b0ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp ra s\u00e2n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Selecao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMarcelo \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb co th\u1eaft c\u01a1 l\u01b0ng trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u0169ng h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c kh\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1edd th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c Marcelo ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a HLV Tite ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m v\u00f2ng knock-out.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Brazil:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-serbia-461-189793.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Serbia 0-2 Brazil (B\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-brazil-vs-serbia-421-189790.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Serbia vs Brazil tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng E World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"650","checkdouble":"189804"},{"date":"06:11 28/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/28/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-serbia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng E VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n- V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Serbia 2-0, Brazil \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a World Cup k\u1ef3 th\u1ee9 13 World Cup, k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1970.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp, Serbia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup trong c\u1ea3 3 VCK h\u1ecd tham d\u1ef1 (2006, 2010 v\u00e0 2018).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Brazil \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2010, khi h\u1ecd to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-Brazil-2-0-Serbia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Brazil 2-0 Serbia gi\u00fap Selecao v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia, Philippe Coutinho \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 6 b\u00e0n trong s\u1ed1 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Brazil trong n\u0103m 2018 (4 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 3 trong s\u1ed1 5 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 t\u1edbi nay c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Coutinho (2 b\u00e0n, 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Neymar hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 8 tr\u1eadn cho Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Neymar v\u00e0 Gabriel Jesus (10) \u0111\u00e3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Brazil d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Tite h\u01a1n Paulinho (8 b\u00e0n).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Aleksandar Mitrovic d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 4 l\u1ea7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia, ch\u1ec9 sau Neymar (7).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Sau 3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, Mitrovic c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 14 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 1 th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Brazil \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 19 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau 24 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Tite (h\u00f2a 4, thua 1), \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 79%.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Thiago Silva t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, \u0111\u1ec1u do Neymar ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o (\u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia n\u0103m 2014).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Serbia 0-2 Brazil\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 0-2 Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Thong-so-Brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Serbia 0-2 Brazil</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Serbia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/brazil-nhan-tin-du-sau-khi-danh-bai-serbia-469-189804.html\">Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-serbia-khang-dinh-choi-tren-chan-brazil-465-189798.html\">HLV Mladen Krstajic: Serbia ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n Brazil trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/danh-bai-mexico-augustinsson-thach-thuc-dt-brazil-465-189787.html\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Mexico, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Brazil</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"649","checkdouble":"189806"},{"date":"17:04 27/06","title":"Man City mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/man-city-muon-gay-soc-voi-nguoi-hung-tuyen-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Reus, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marco Reus \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Reus kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho Dortmund. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Reus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Reus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/man-city-muon-gay-soc-voi-nguoi-hung-tuyen-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marco Reus \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Marco Reus \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c khi ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarco Reus \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Man City chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Marco Reus</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport Bild, Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Marco Reus, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham muon gay soc voi Marco Reus\" title=\"Tottenham mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Marco Reus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/2/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-marco-reus.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City mu\u1ed1n chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Marco Reus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola v\u1eabn \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-nang-gia-hoi-mua-mahrez-len-75-trieu-bang-172-187268.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City quan t\u00e2m Mahrez</span> ho\u1eb7c Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 2 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111i v\u00e0o b\u1ebf t\u1eafc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nZaha s\u1eafp gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Palace trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Leicester h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 90 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Mahrez. Sport Bild kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City s\u1ebd t\u1eeb b\u1ecf hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Marco Reus c\u1ee7a Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Dortmund c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Man xanh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"648","checkdouble":"189750"},{"date":"16:40 27/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 27/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 27/6.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb l\u1ed7i, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-463-189755.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP MEXICO VS TH\u1ee4Y \u0110I\u1ec2N</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"647","checkdouble":"189755"},{"date":"16:44 27/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c 21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-duc-vs-han-quoc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Matteo Darmian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matteo Darmian s\u1eafp r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMatteo Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn MU t\u1eeb Torino, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u. Vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mua Matteo Darmian c\u1ee7a MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/30/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matteo Darmian mu\u1ed1n chia tay MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n Darmian b\u1ecb t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ra \u0111i c\u00e0ng s\u1edbm c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-thua-nhan-darmian-sap-roi-mu-172-176855.html\" target=\"_blank\">Matteo Darmian c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU</span>, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 r\u1eddi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Darmian</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Matteo Darmian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U can giu chan hau ve Darmian\" title=\"M.U can giu chan hau ve Darmian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/29/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-ngay-16-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Darmian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSky Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Darmian, h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng qua \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 MU thu v\u1ec1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Roma, Napoli hay Inter Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Darmian, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi Juventus, b\u1edfi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Darmian \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Paratici c\u1ee7a Juventus, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 s\u1eafp \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U, Darmian kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Italia \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"646","checkdouble":"189757"},{"date":"17:32 27/06","title":"MU v\u00e0 Arsenal chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua \"Ronaldo H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/mu-va-arsenal-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Son Heung-Min r\u1eddi Tottenham, Sport 1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Son Heung-Min \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Tottenham, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Son Heung-Min \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Pochettino, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Spurs.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU v\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Son Heung-Min r\u1eddi Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU v\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Son Heung-Min r\u1eddi Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/mu-va-arsenal-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-han-quoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Son Heung-Min \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 27 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Dele Alli, Christian Eriksen l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba ch\u01a1i ph\u00eda sau trung phong Harry Kane.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Son Heung-Min l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Tottenham c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf Premier League trong v\u00e0i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ghi 47 b\u00e0n sau 139 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Son Heung-Min c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111ang c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU v\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Son Heung-Min</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m. MU v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Son Heung-Min r\u1eddi Tottenham, Sport 1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Son Heung-Min\" title=\"Son Heung-Min\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Du-am-Thuy-Dien-1-0-Han-Quoc-Son-Heung-min-gay-that-vong--hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU v\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Son Heung-Min</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 HLV Emery c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-189764.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/30/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ngoi-sao-dau-tien-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-189764.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Matteo Darmian th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nHLV Pochettino mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-troi-chan-ronaldo-han-quoc-172-182334.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Son</span>,&nbsp;\u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Spurs kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong c\u00f9ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"645","checkdouble":"189762"},{"date":"17:19 27/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng xem Brazil vs Serbia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-serbia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-serbia-vs-brazil.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia v\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebb th\u1eafng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn 90 ph\u00fat tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Otkrytiye Arena s\u1ebd c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\n- <strong>C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>Brazil th\u1eafng 2-1</strong></div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u:</em> Brazil vs Serbia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 1h ng\u00e0y 28/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Otkrytiye Arena (Moskva)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Brazil -0.95*0:1*0.90 Serbia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u 0.90*2 3/4*-0.97 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o, t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean gia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-brazil-vs-serbia-va-du-doan-soi-keo-serbia-vs-brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia 1h ng\u00e0y 28/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil, kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng Brazil s\u1ebd b\u1ecb Costa Rica c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang sau 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Nh\u01b0ng ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eadp nh\u1ea3 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Gabriel Jesus, Philippe Coutinho xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. 6 ph\u00fat sau, Neymar \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Brazil th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi khi b\u1ecb Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1. Nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Costa Rica b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, cho t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 68 Brazil chuy\u1ec3n qua 4-2-4 v\u1edbi Coutinho \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ea1nh m\u1ecf neo Casemiro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica\" title=\"Neymar Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Vi-dieu-nay,-Brazil-van-la-ung-vien-vo-dich-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil m\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 Costa Rica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3, Brazil d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n sang 3-3-4 v\u1edbi Casemiro, Thiago Silva v\u00e0 Miranda \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 Marcelo v\u00e0 Fagner d\u00e2ng cao nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Costa Rica r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c Coutinho \u0111\u1ed9t ng\u1ed9t x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV Tite c\u0169ng ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Brazil. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Douglas Costa xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n thay cho Willian. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Juventus r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi qu\u1ea5y r\u1ed1i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Costa Rica kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, m\u1edf ra kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho ghi ban mo ty so cho Brazil\" title=\"Coutinho ghi ban mo ty so cho Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c Roberto Firmino v\u00e0o thay Paulinho c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Brazil nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n b\u00ean trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Costa Rica \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Brazil c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRi\u00eang khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica gi\u00fap Brazil r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh 2 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n anh gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa s\u1ee9c \u00e9p m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap Selecao c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-thang-tran-world-cup-dau-tien-le-tru-ta-bat-dau-421-189322.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/brazil-thang-tran-world-cup-dau-tien-le-tru-ta-bat-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-thang-tran-world-cup-dau-tien-le-tru-ta-bat-dau-421-189322.html\">Brazil th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean: L\u1ec5 tr\u1eeb t\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u\u2026</span><br>\r\n<span>T\u1eebng ph\u00fat t\u1eebng gi\u00e2y c\u1ee9 d\u1ea7n tr\u00f4i \u1edf St. Petersburg, hi\u1ec3m h\u1ecda b\u00f3ng ma k\u00e9o \u0111\u1ebfn cho\u00e1ng t\u1eebng m\u1ea3ng t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m kinh...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBrazil c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 nh\u01b0ng h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u2013 b\u1ea1i (+2 so v\u1edbi +1). C\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean Serbia \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Brazil. C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 2.5 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u1edf n\u00ean khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. Gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y n\u00f3 l\u00ean 2.75 b\u00e0n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ee3p l\u00fd khi m\u00e0 Serbia b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 cho \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean th\u1ee9 2 n\u1ebfu Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t h\u00e3n h\u1eefu v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ea3y ch\u00e2n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mladen Krstajic c\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 c\u1ee9u m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3 s\u1eed n\u1ebfu Serbia ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a l\u00e0 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Brazil vs Serbia s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mong ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: </strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (O 2 3/4)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u1edf tr\u00ean. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ngay nh\u1eefng l\u00fac b\u1ebf t\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Neymar, Willian hay Coutinho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Selecao t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Serbia thang Thuy Si\" title=\"Serbia thang Thuy Si\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Serbia-thang-Thuy-Si.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Serbia c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Serbia. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o d\u00f9 l\u00e0 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn. Serbia c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Adem Ljajic, Dusan Tadic, Alex Kolarov t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Alek Mitrovic, Milinkovic-Savic, Nemanja Matic, Nicola Milenkovic, Branislav Ivanovic \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, Kolarov, Ljajic, Tadic, Milivojevic \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng. R\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea7m xa, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao. 15 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eeba qua, ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn Serbia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn:</strong> Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn</h2>\r\n- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1edf l\u00ean)<br>\r\n- <strong>C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi</strong><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>Brazil th\u1eafng 2-1</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c</h2>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Serbia t\u1eeb 6 tr\u1edf l\u00ean (O 6)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Serbia s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Brazil (-1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc-421-189718.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-duc-vs-han-quoc-va-du-doan-soi-keo-han-quoc-vs-duc-421-189718.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u00f4i s\u1ee5c cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\n<span>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi 90 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-duc-vs-han-quoc-463-189757.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-duc-vs-han-quoc.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-duc-vs-han-quoc-463-189757.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c 21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs \u0110\u1ee9c: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-463-189755.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-mexico-vs-thuy-dien-463-189755.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 21h00 ng\u00e0y 27/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Mexico vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"644","checkdouble":"189763"}]}